short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI assisted MOT and Tax lookup for UK car registrations

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Hey Reg is a new way to get a car's MOT data in 1 click. If you see an image with a car and clearly visible UK registration number, just right click and hit the "Hey Reg üëç" option in the context menu!
